sentences: Siri Beathe Gellein (born 1 October 1966 in Trondheim, Norway) is a Norwegian Musician (vocals) and journalist, known from several albums, bands and television programs.
Her own Siri's Svale Band (established in 1987) performs ("sval") cool jazz, with soul.
The Quintet released the album Blackbird (1990) and Necessarily So ... (2001) at label Sonor Records.
